* Desmonus watched as the remainder of the Alliance flew off in persuite of 
the enemy, her growling stomach causing her to sigh and look around. She was 
SO very hungry, and there were plenty of feeding oppertunities around but 
none to her taste.
She looked around and was still able to smell that wounded bot who she 
wished to feed on later, her stomach growling yet again.
But then, all of a sudden her com-link came alive with her masters voice.
She looks up and sees him flying towards her, speading up a bit and 
responding.*

" Yes, of course I would wish to come with you, Lord."
